sequenceDiagram
    participant EV as event.cpp or editing_controller
    participant SM as state_machine
    participant DS as DocState
    participant VAL as validate and invariants

    EV->>SM: state_begin_event_cascade cause
    SM->>DS: set active_event_log and bump cascade_depth
    SM->>DS: state_begin_batch sets s_in_batch true

    Note right of DS: mutation-time asserts now suppressed

    EV->>DS: transition APIs and doc_state_set_ mutate fields
    DS->>DS: state_set bumps version and marks dirty
    DS->>DS: assert skipped while in batch or cascade

    EV->>SM: state_end_event_cascade
    SM->>DS: state_end_batch clears s_in_batch and runs assert once
    SM->>VAL: radiant_state_settle validate interaction
    VAL->>DS: sm_derive_state per invariant binding
    VAL-->>SM: state.validated or state.invalid plus snapshot
    SM->>SM: radiant_state_dump_emit_cascade diffable Mark tree
    SM->>DS: decrement cascade_depth and clear log at zero
